{"metadata":{"fragments":[{"text":"func","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"stop"},{"text":"()","kind":"text"}],"title":"stop()","externalID":"s:3GIO21SocketServiceProtocolPAAE4stopyyF::SYNTHESIZED::s:3GIO13SocketServiceC","extendedModule":"GIO","roleHeading":"Instance Method","modules":[{"name":"GIO"}],"symbolKind":"method","role":"symbol"},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"stop"},{"text":"()","kind":"text"}],"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["macOS"]}]},{"content":[{"level":2,"anchor":"discussion","type":"heading","text":"Discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This call is thread-safe, so it may be called from a thread"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"handling an incoming client request."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Note that this only stops accepting new connections; it does not"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"close the listening sockets, and you can call"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_socket_service_start()"},{"type":"text","text":" again later to begin listening again. To"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"close the listening sockets, call ","type":"text"},{"code":"g_socket_listener_close()","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":". (This","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"will happen automatically when the "},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/SocketService","type":"reference"},{"text":" is finalized.)","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This must be called before calling "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"g_socket_listener_close()"},{"type":"text","text":" as"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"the socket service will start accepting connections immediately"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"when a new socket is added."}]}],"kind":"content"}],"sections":[],"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/gio\/socketservice\/stop()"]}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/SocketService\/stop()","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"text":"Stops the service, i.e. stops accepting connections","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"from the added sockets when the mainloop runs."}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/SocketService","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/SocketService\/SocketServiceProtocol-Implementations"]]},"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"references":{"doc://GIO/documentation/GIO/SocketService/stop()":{"url":"\/documentation\/gio\/socketservice\/stop()","title":"stop()","abstract":[{"text":"Stops the service, i.e. stops accepting connections","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"from the added sockets when the mainloop runs.","type":"text"}],"role":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/SocketService\/stop()","type":"topic","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"stop"},{"kind":"text","text":"()"}],"kind":"symbol"},"doc://GIO/documentation/GIO/SocketService/SocketServiceProtocol-Implementations":{"url":"\/documentation\/gio\/socketservice\/socketserviceprotocol-implementations","kind":"article","type":"topic","role":"collectionGroup","abstract":[],"identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/SocketService\/SocketServiceProtocol-Implementations","title":"SocketServiceProtocol Implementations"},"doc://GIO/documentation/GIO/SocketService":{"type":"topic","title":"SocketService","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"SocketService"}],"url":"\/documentation\/gio\/socketservice","identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/SocketService","kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"class","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"SocketService","kind":"identifier"}],"abstract":[{"text":"A ","type":"text"},{"code":"GSocketService","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" is an object that represents a service that"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"is provided to the network or over local sockets.  When a new","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"connection is made to the service the [signal[SocketService](\/\/documentation\/gio\/socketservice\/onincoming(flags:handler:)]","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"signal is emitted.","type":"text"}],"role":"symbol"},"doc://GIO/documentation/GIO":{"type":"topic","abstract":[],"identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO","title":"GIO","url":"\/documentation\/gio","role":"collection","kind":"symbol"}}}